*
 * 使用洗牌算法打乱数组的顺序，并输出新的数组
 *
 * @function
 * @memberof Fx
 * @see https://bost.ocks.org/mike/shuffle/
 * @see https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fisher-Yates_shuffle
 * @param  {Any[]} arr 待打乱顺序的数组
 * @returns {Any[]}
 * @example
 *
 * const list = [1, 2, 3, 4];
 * console.log(Fx.shuffle(list));
 * console.log(Fx.shuffle(list));
